            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-1063] Dubious synchronization in Zookeeper and ClientCnxnSocketNIO classes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1063</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Synchronization around dataWatches, existWatches and childWatches in Zookeeper is incorrect.&lt;br/&gt;
Synchronization around outgoingQueue and pendingQueue in ClientCnxnSocketNIO is incorrect.&lt;br/&gt;
Synchronization around selector and key sets in ClientCnxnSocketNIO seems odd.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
